# Inline Button Syntax

Default button: <gno-button href="https://example.com" content="Submit"/>

Outline button: <gno-button href="https://example.com" content="Info" variant="outline"/>

Caution button: <gno-button href="https://example.com" content="Delete" variant="caution"/>

Warning button: <gno-button href="https://example.com" content="Warning" variant="warning"/>

Info button: <gno-button href="https://example.com" content="Details" variant="info"/>

Note button: <gno-button href="https://example.com" content="Note" variant="note"/>

Multiple variants: <gno-button href="https://example.com" content="Delete" variant="caution outline"/>

